<section class="boxheader" id="azure">
    <div class="box">
        <h2 class="hidden" style="font-size: 3rem; color: #222323;">Working Towards a Low-Friction Future</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
        <p>A technology driven way to hire and retain freelancers. Pay freelancers in an ethical and sustainable way with the lowest possible platform fees.
            Utilizing a blockchain solution with low environmental impact, and a proven decade of 24/7 payments.<br /><br /></p>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="splashimage" id="azure">
    <h2 class="abouttitle textcenter abouttitledropdown" id="aboutlist" onclick="toggleDisplay('techabout')">Technology &#10549;</h2>
    <div id="techabout" style="display: none;">
        <div class="box" id="azure">
            <div class="spacer">
            </div>
            <div class="boxheader" id="azure">
                <div class="box">
                    <img src="/images/XRPSymbol.png" class="hidden" id="logo" alt="xrp symbol">
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter hidden">The XRP Ledger</h2>
                    <p>Using distributed ledger technology, the XRP Ledger allows instant and seamless payments between users.
                        On Volera the Escrow feature allows secure and promised movement of payments between clients and freelancers.<br><br>
                        Learn more about the XRP Ledger at xrpl.org</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter hidden">Escrow Payments</h2>
                    <p>
                        As a native feature of the XRPL funds can be stored in a temporary locked account that the hiring enterprise or oracle retains a key to. Once the job is confirmed to be completed, they send the key to the freelancer to release the escrowed funds.
                        Never share this key with anyone that you don't want to receive the funds.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter hidden">Send Payments</h2>
                    <p>Send funds directly to other users across the XRPL anytime instantly. Can be used for smaller jobs that do not require the security of escrow.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter hidden">Hooks</h2>
                    <p>Using the XRPL Labs proposed ammendment and the XUMM Wallet, we plan to implement layer-one smart contracts into Volera's escrow features. Providing very lightweight logic on the XRPL, and eventually within Volera's ecosystem.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2 class="textcenter hidden">Check Balance</h2>
                    <p>Immediately see when funds are deposited into your account, keep track of all payments from anywhere with your mobile device.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="https://xrpl.org/xrp-ledger-overview.html"><h4 class="textcenter wave4">Learn More About the XRP Ledger</h4></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="abouttitle abouttitledropdown textcenter" id="aboutlist" onclick="toggleDisplay('userabout')">Users &#10549;</h2>
    <div id="userabout" style="display: none;">
        <div class="boxheader">
            <div class="box">
                <h2 class="hidden textcenter">Freelancers</h2>
                <p>With no membership fees our platform is free to explore and build a profile. Showcase your best projects and techinical abilites to attract hiring enterprises and land your next contract. 
                    Upload your resume or CV and start applying for jobs as soon as Volera is live. <br><br>
                    Freelancing here you can keep your rates the same as any other platform, while receiving more of the total payout with our low 5% fee across all completed jobs. That means more money in your pocket. Work contracts as an individual or as a studio full of creators.
                <br><br></p>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <h2 class="hidden textcenter">Enterprises</h2>
                <p>A frictionless experience for startups and fortune 500 companies to easily integrate Volera into their hiring avenues. With a 0 fee structure for any hiring enterprise or individual.<br><br>
                Create contracts, have a budget for a portion of your project, and  </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="abouttitle abouttitledropdown textcenter" id="aboutlist" onclick="toggleDisplay('walletabout')">Mobile Wallet &#10549;</h2>
    <div id="walletabout" style="display: none;">
        <div class="box" id="azure">  
            <div class="boxheader">
                <div class="box">
                    <img src="/images/xumm-icon.png" class="hidden" id="logo" alt="xumm logo">
                    <p>Required to fully utilize the Volera Platform. XUMM is the integrated wallet on Volera that allows the use of technical aspects of the underlying XRPL technology.<br><br>
                        Instant payments, User IDs, escrow, high-security, and self-custody. </p>
                    <a class="button link textcenter hidden" href="https://xumm.app/">Learn More</a>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden box" id="image">
                    <img src="/images/xummcell.png" id="xumm" alt="xumm shown on a mobile device">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
